@host = http://localhost:5000

### Listar servi√ßos
GET {{host}}/api/services
Accept: application/json

### Consultar slots
@serviceId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{host}}/api/slots?serviceId={{serviceId}}&date=2025-08-30
Accept: application/json

### Criar agendamento
POST {{host}}/api/book
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "serviceId": "{{serviceId}}",
  "startUtc": "2025-08-30T12:00:00Z",
  "clientName": "Cliente Teste",
  "clientContact": "(11) 99999-0000"
}

### Cancelar agendamento
POST {{host}}/api/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
  "reason": "Cliente solicitou cancelamento"
}

### Status do dia
GET {{host}}/api/status-dia?date=2025-08-30
Accept: application/json

### Atualizar status (CheckIn, InService, Done, NoShow, Cancelled)
@appointmentId = 33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333
POST {{host}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/status/CheckIn
X-User: admin

